Metadata.Title: The Great Grape
Metadata.Description: Your objective is to eliminate five winery workers stationed in the grape fields. Each target must be discreetly taken out using a grape knife to maintain the illusion of an accident. Utilize the environment to your advantage; blend in with the vineyard landscape, and consider manipulating distractions or using stealth to avoid detection. Plan your approach carefully, ensuring a swift exit after completing your mission to evade any potential witnesses or security personnel.
